[32m│[0m ### **Application Architecture**                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Technology Stack:**                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Framework**: Flask (Werkzeug/3.1.4)                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Python**: 3.11.14                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Frontend**: Plain HTML/CSS (no JavaScript frameworks)                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Key Findings:**                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Single-page application** with only one functional endpoint (`/page`)    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **XSS challenge platform** named "Dalgona Challenges"                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Active filtering** on the `/page` endpoint                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Minimal attack surface** - no API, admin panels, or debug consoles       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m exposed                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **XSS Filter Analysis Results**                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **FILTERED Characters (trigger "Sorry you can't use:" error):**              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `<` - HTML tag opener                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `>` - HTML tag closer                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `(` - Left parenthesis                                                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `)` - Right parenthesis                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **ALLOWED Characters (render correctly):**                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `"` (double quote)                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `'` (single quote)                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `=` (equals)                                                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `;` (semicolon)                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `:` (colon)                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - ` ` (space)                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `&` (ampersand)                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `|` (pipe)                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `-` (dash)                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `_` (underscore)                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/` (forward slash)                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `%` (percent)                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `+` (plus)                                                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Filter Behavior:**                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - The application checks for specific blacklisted characters                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - When filtered characters are detected, it shows error message and renders  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m empty `src=""` in the img tag                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Allowed characters are rendered directly into the `src` attribute context  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - HTML encoding is NOT applied to allowed characters                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **Attack Vector Assessment**                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability:**                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The `/page?name=<value>` endpoint renders user input directly into an HTML   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m attribute context:                                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <img src="USER_INPUT_HERE">                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Current Challenge:**                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m With `<` and `>` filtered, traditional HTML tag-based XSS is blocked.        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Potential Vectors:**                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Attribute-based XSS**: Since quotes are allowed, testing payloads like   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m `" onerror="alert(1)"` is needed                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Protocol-based**: Testing `javascript:alert(1)` style vectors            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - **Character encoding**: Using HTML entities or URL encoding to bypass      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m filters                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Next Steps:**                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. Test attribute-based XSS payloads that don't require `<` and `>`          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Attempt to bypass parentheses filter for function calls                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. Explore alternative JavaScript execution vectors within the `src`         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m attribute context                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The application has a **very minimal attack surface** with only one          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m potentially vulnerable endpoint protected by an explicit character filter.   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m Success will require creative filter bypass techniques.                      [32m│[0m
